text: Knowledgeable barista who recommended great tasting &  lovely looking houjicha, genmaicha, matcha & dirty lattes. Loved their tiramisu & affogato too!
Had one of the best coffee and houjicha latte in town! Joshua is so passionate about the coffee he made! Worth the 5 star rating!
I drink about 2 cups of really good coffee from Gobi everyday. Also look forward to the weekends when there are treats like tiramisu & affogato.
Fantastic coffee, knowledgeable barista who's always happy to share more about what you're drinking (and some say he is pretty good-looking)!
How lucky are we at Parc Esta to have our very own barista? Thank you Joshua for sharing your love for coffee with us!
